Project registration copies template structures into:
* PROJECTROADMAPS
* PROJECTROADMAPMILESTONES
* PROJECTROADMAPACTIVITIES
* PROJECTROADMAPACTIVITYPREREQS

== Common Data Patterns ==
* Audit fields are common: CREATEDBY/DATE, MODIFIEDBY/DATE, TRANSACTIONKEY, ISACTIVE
* ID strategy is mixed:
** business keys for many masters (for example PLANTCODE, CATEGORYCODE, MODULECODE)
** SYS_GUID-style VARCHAR2 identifiers for many operational entities
* Status values include NOT STARTED, ONGOING, CANCELLED, CLOSED (HOLD appears for projects)
* CLOB columns store rich-text/dynamic payloads (notes, options, values, etc.)

